| Issue                                                | Why it's a problem                         | Fix                                   |
| ---------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------- |
| `getPriority` recreated each render                  | Minor CPU overhead                         | Move outside component                |
| Filter logic uses undefined `lhsPriority`            | Likely runtime error                       | Use proper variable `balancePriority` |
| `filter` + `sort` calls `getPriority` multiple times | Redundant computation                      | Compute priority once per balance     |
| `formattedBalances` unused                           | Wasteful computation                       | Either use it or remove               |
| `rows` maps over unformatted balances                | Recomputes USD & formatting each render    | Precompute in `useMemo`               |
| `key={index}`                                        | React may reuse DOM incorrectly            | Use unique key (`currency`)           |
| `useMemo` depends on `prices` object                 | Object reference changes trigger recompute | Use stable values or memoize `prices` |
| `any` and missing interface fields                   | Type safety issues                         | Use proper types                      |
